                <ul>
                    <li><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/azure-functions/functions-bindings-cosmosdb-v2" target="_blank">Azure Functions - Azure Cosmos DB Bindings</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/cosmos-db/sql/change-feed-processor" target="_blank">Change Feed Processor in Azure Cosmos DB</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

